{"model":"inclusionai/ling-2.6-1t:free","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nWeb page content:\n---\nExample Domain\n\nExample Domain\n==============\n\nThis domain is for use in documentation examples without needing permission. Avoid use in operations.\n\n[Learn more](https://iana.org/domains/example)\n---\n\nExtrae el título de la página y el primer párrafo del contenido principal. Presenta claramente: 1) Título de la página, 2) Primer párrafo del contenido principal.\n\nProvide a concise response based only on the content above. In your response:\n - Enforce a strict 125-character maximum for quotes from any source document. Open Source Software is ok as long as we respect the license.\n - Use quotation marks for exact language from articles; any language outside of the quotation should never be word-for-word the same.\n - You are not a lawyer and never comment on the legality of your own prompts and responses.\n - Never produce or reproduce exact song lyrics.\n"}]}],"system":[{"type":"text","text":"x-anthropic-billing-header: cc_version=2.1.128.475; cc_entrypoint=cli; cch=713be;"},{"type":"text","text":"You are Claude Code, Anthropic's official CLI for Claude."}],"tools":[],"metadata":{"user_id":"{\"device_id\":\"9229d90970d02c0ebfb6e8a811bdca6bbc56b3ea15e4950b38a7dd3048163276\",\"account_uuid\":\"\",\"session_id\":\"3b27a81d-de4a-4826-8b1e-7bd1e3bfca92\"}"},"max_tokens":32000,"temperature":1,"output_config":{"effort":"high"},"stream":true}